 Liked the location: it’s so easy to walk to the station and all airport terminals; luggage trolleys were available outside the hotel doors (cost £1); 
My (superior) room was extremely clean and well maintained; I slept well and did not hear any hotel noise, I had a view of the airport. 
Staff were pleasant.

